---
title: Sage-Butter Roasted Pork with Roasted Butternut Squash & Charred Broccolini
description: Sage adds earthy depth to honeyed squash and juicy pro chops in this Instgram-worth dish. Roasting the broccolini helps developed crispy edges and a nutty flavor - try with regular broccoli too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54f5dafa6ced6e1f358b456a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/54f5dafa6ced6e1f358b456a.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sage-butter-roasted-pork-54f5dafa6ced6e1f358b456a
